This is another classic, folks. The old deflect everything away from myself. Assume no responsibility for my actions. Downplay everything, it was someone else who made me do it. Who me? Cast the first stone?  <br><br>
Maintaining the &quot;superior&quot; fantasy world is interesting. It is going to be tough to continue because he will run out of fantasies real soon. The Ritz Carlton, the cigars, the CEO on the street, the &quot;uplink&quot;, and all the rest of the stuff is pure fantasy. Motive? Who knows. Only an accomplished and experienced mental health professional knows for sure, and then I am not sure it is really important for us to know or care. It is clear that the fantasy of superiority is operationally important. Lets see how long he can keep it up. The mental energy expended must be fantastic!<br><br>
I find particularly interesting the downplay of his comments on the juvenile female! No normal person would even have those thoughts cross his mind, much less make them up! I can opine that they were a real expression that accidentally slipped by in the heat of the moment exposing the true nature of the individual. All the key words are there, in the right order, no less! This aspect will be worth watching. It is not that he has hit anyone's molester nerve ending, it is that some people may see a pedophile component in him! Unbelieveable!<br><br>
Oh, boy!<br><br>
This is really going to be a trip from now on. I will tell everyone again, electrically grounded spaghetti colanders and four cloves of garlic!<br><br>
